Description_lang: While above $s4% health and in combat, you enter a Dreaming Trance and gain $s2 Critical Strike. The trance will deepen every second and grant another stack, up to $420834U.If you drop below $s4% health, a burst of Dreamtender's Pollen will slow nearby enemies by $s3% for $420762d and prevent Dreaming Trance for $420812d. Dreaming Trance will linger for 1 sec per Ysemerald you have socketed into your gear.
